###
###
###
# ─── #tt-Doodles EMOJIS ───
# Doodle trait-tier star emojis — one shown per trait slot in the doodle list.
# Tier ranking (best → worst):
#   Perfect = Rarely Tired in the first slot
#   Amazing = Rarely Tired in any other slot
#   Great   = Always Affectionate/Playful + all Rarely-positive traits
#   Good    = Often Affectionate/Playful, Pretty Calm/Excitable
#   OK      = Rarely Affectionate/Playful + all Sometimes traits
#   Bad     = every Always/Often negative trait
#
# Perfect and Amazing share the same star emoji by default — the tier label
# in brackets ("[Perfect]" vs "[Amazing]") distinguishes them visually.
STAR_PERFECT=<:RBStar:1497375968619135076>
STAR_AMAZING=<:RBStar:1497375968619135076>
STAR_GREAT=<:GoldenStar:1497383695781462016>
STAR_GOOD=<:SilverStar:1497299363590967549>
STAR_OK=<:BronzeStar:1497300707554889891>
STAR_BAD=<:Trash:1497379832865226844>
